Electric Winter/Xmas!
==================

### This map contains:

- HDR

- Santa

- Soccer

- Pool

- SoccerDisco

- Crate climbing

- Loads of secrets

- Snow!

- Santa's workshop

- Presents

- 64 slots

- Improved armory

- And much more!

Information
------------------

This map started as a project for a specific community, but it closed down. So I decided to release it here for everyone to use.
